sequenceDiagram
    participant WT1 as Worktree Agent 1
    participant WT2 as Worktree Agent 2
    participant MQ as Merge Queue<br>merge-queue.jsonl
    participant PL as Primary Loop
    participant GIT as Git Repository

    Note over WT1,WT2: Parallel execution in isolated worktrees

    WT1->>WT1: Execute hat iterations
    WT2->>WT2: Execute hat iterations

    WT1->>MQ: enqueue(loop-id-1, prompt)
    Note over MQ: Event: Queued { prompt }

    WT2->>WT2: Still working...

    PL->>MQ: next_pending()
    MQ-->>PL: Entry: loop-id-1

    PL->>MQ: mark_merging(loop-id-1, pid)
    Note over MQ: Event: Merging { pid }

    PL->>GIT: git merge worktree branch
    alt No Conflicts
        GIT-->>PL: Merge successful
        PL->>MQ: mark_merged(loop-id-1, commit-sha)
        Note over MQ: Event: Merged { commit }
        PL->>GIT: remove_worktree(loop-id-1)
    else Conflicts Detected
        GIT-->>PL: Merge conflict
        PL->>PL: Spawn merge-ralph agent
        PL->>GIT: Resolve conflicts
        PL->>MQ: mark_merged(loop-id-1, commit-sha)
        PL->>GIT: remove_worktree(loop-id-1)
    end

    WT2->>MQ: enqueue(loop-id-2, prompt)
    Note over MQ: Event: Queued { prompt }

    PL->>MQ: next_pending()
    MQ-->>PL: Entry: loop-id-2

    PL->>MQ: mark_merging(loop-id-2, pid)
    PL->>GIT: git merge worktree branch
    GIT-->>PL: Merge successful
    PL->>MQ: mark_merged(loop-id-2, commit-sha)
    PL->>GIT: remove_worktree(loop-id-2)

    Note over MQ: Full event history preserved<br>in append-only JSONL
